name: Lemonglass Bracelet
description:
This bracelet was designed to be happy and beautiful, yet also understated. An ideal staple for brightly-colored outfits, but can also produce a nice splash of color against darker clothes as well. Findings are sterling silver, diamond beads are beautiful Swarovski crystals, and the round beads are varnished Sculpey. Measures approx. 7.7"

name: BLUprint Collection
description:
Inspired by Chinese porcelain, this set features a heavenly blend of blue and pearl-white. On the bracelet are blue-and-white swirled teardrops, and the earrings are little blue-and-white swirled fishes. Both pieces are topped off with blue and white Swarovski crystal beads for a tranquil, yet fashion-forward look. Bracelet: sterling silver findings, Swarovski crystal beads, teardrop beads handmade with Sculpey. Earrings: sterling silver findings, Swarovski crystal beads, fishes handmade with Sculpey. Bracelet measures approx. 7.6"
